{"tha-ap42:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap42:0.2":"Kundadhanavagga ","tha-ap42:0.3":"Kapparukkhiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap42:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap42:1.2":"thupasetthassa sammukha; ","tha-ap42:1.3":"Vicittadusse lagetva, ","tha-ap42:1.4":"kapparukkham thapesaham. ","tha-ap42:2.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap42:2.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap42:2.3":"Sobhayanto mama dvaram, ","tha-ap42:2.4":"kapparukkho patitthati. ","tha-ap42:3.1":"Ahanca parisa ceva, ","tha-ap42:3.2":"ye keci mama vassita; ","tha-ap42:3.3":"Tamha dussam gahetvana, ","tha-ap42:3.4":"nivasema mayam sada. ","tha-ap42:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap42:4.2":"yam rukkham thapayim aham; ","tha-ap42:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap42:4.4":"kapparukkhassidam phalam. ","tha-ap42:5.1":"Ito ca sattame kappe, ","tha-ap42:5.2":"sucela attha khattiya; ","tha-ap42:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap42:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap42:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap42:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap42:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap42:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kapparukkhiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap42:8.1":"Kapparukkhiyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap42:9.1":"Kundadhanavaggo catuttho. ","tha-ap42:10.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap42:11.1":"Kundasagatakaccana, ","tha-ap42:11.2":"udayi mogharajako; ","tha-ap42:11.3":"Adhimutto lasunado, ","tha-ap42:11.4":"ayagi dhammacakkiko; ","tha-ap42:11.5":"Kapparukkhi ca dasamo, ","tha-ap42:11.6":"gatha dvayadasasatam. "}